---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="VibeWeave - 音乐情绪分析平台"
  description="通过AI技术分析音乐情绪，帮助你发现音乐背后的情感密码，创建更符合你心情的播放列表"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 md:py-32">
    <!-- Background gradient -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0F0F0F] via-[#1E3A8A] to-[#4C1D95]"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_50%,rgba(139,92,246,0.15),transparent_70%)]"></div>

    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-8">
        <!-- Badge -->
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-vibe-purple/20 border border-vibe-purple/40 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm text-white">
          <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
            <span class="absolute inline-flex h-full w-full animate-ping rounded-full bg-vibe-purple opacity-75"></span>
            <span class="relative inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-vibe-purple"></span>
          </span>
          AI 驱动的音乐情绪分析
        </div>

        <!-- Heading -->
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold leading-tight max-w-4xl">
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-vibe-purple via-vibe-blue to-vibe-pink text-transparent bg-clip-text drop-shadow-lg">
            感受音乐的 情绪脉搏
          </span>
          <br />
          <span class="text-white">VibeWeave — 音乐情绪编织师</span>
        </h1>

        <!-- Description -->
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl">
          通过先进的AI技术分析音乐情绪，帮助你发现每首歌背后的情感密码，创建更符合你心情的播放列表，让音乐与情绪完美融合。
        </p>

        <!-- CTA Input -->
        <div class="w-full max-w-2xl">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <input
                type="url"
                placeholder="粘贴网易云音乐歌单链接..."
                class="w-full h-14 rounded-full border border-gray-600 bg-black/30 backdrop-blur-sm text-white placeholder-gray-400 px-6 focus:outline-none focus:border-vibe-purple transition-colors"
              />
            </div>
            <a
              href="/dashboard"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-14 px-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-vibe-purple to-vibe-blue hover:from-vibe-blue hover:to-vibe-purple transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg hover:shadow-vibe-purple/30 text-white font-medium"
            >
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19V6l12-3v13M9 19c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zm12-3c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zM9 10l12-3" />
              </svg>
              开始分析
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Secondary CTA -->
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a
            href="#features"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 h-12 px-6 rounded-full border border-gray-600 text-white hover:border-vibe-purple hover:text-vibe-purple transition-all duration-300"
          >
            <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
            了解更多
            <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <section id="features" class="relative py-20 bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-sm border-t border-gray-800">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 flex flex-col gap-12">
      <!-- Section Header -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-vibe-purple/20 border border-vibe-purple/40 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm text-vibe-purple">
            核心功能
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">
            探索音乐的情感世界
          </h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          利用AI技术，深入分析音乐的情绪特征，为你提供全新的音乐体验
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Features Grid -->
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        {[
          {
            icon: 'heart',
            title: '音乐情绪分析',
            description: '基于AI技术，分析每首歌曲的情绪特征，包括快乐、悲伤、愤怒、平静等多种情绪维度'
          },
          {
            icon: 'layers',
            title: '多平台歌单导入',
            description: '支持从网易云音乐、QQ音乐、Spotify等平台导入歌单，一键分析所有歌曲的情绪特征'
          },
          {
            icon: 'bar-chart',
            title: '情绪可视化',
            description: '通过直观的图表和色彩，展示歌曲的情绪分布，让你更直观地了解音乐的情感表达'
          },
          {
            icon: 'thumbs-up',
            title: '智能歌单推荐',
            description: '根据你的情绪状态和音乐偏好，智能推荐符合你当前心情的歌曲和歌单'
          },
          {
            icon: 'tag',
            title: '情绪标签管理',
            description: '为歌曲添加自定义情绪标签，创建属于你自己的情绪音乐库，更精准地管理音乐'
          },
          {
            icon: 'refresh',
            title: '多设备同步',
            description: '在不同设备间同步你的歌单和情绪分析结果，随时随地享受个性化的音乐体验'
          }
        ].map((feature, index) => (
          <div
            key={index}
            class="h-full border border-gray-800 bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:border-vibe-purple/40 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-vibe-purple/5 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer"
          >
            <div class="p-6">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-vibe-purple/20 to-vibe-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center text-vibe-purple shrink-0">
                  <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    {feature.icon === 'heart' && <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />}
                    {feature.icon === 'layers' && <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />}
                    {feature.icon === 'bar-chart' && <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />}
                    {feature.icon === 'thumbs-up' && <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M14 10h4.764a2 2 0 011.789 2.894l-3.5 7A2 2 0 0115.263 21h-4.017c-.163 0-.326-.02-.485-.06L7 20m7-10V5a2 2 0 00-2-2h-.095c-.5 0-.905.405-.905.905 0 .714-.211 1.412-.608 2.006L7 11v9m7-10h-2M7 20H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2h2.5" />}
                    {feature.icon === 'tag' && <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z" />}
                    {feature.icon === 'refresh' && <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15" />}
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                  <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2">{feature.title}</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                    {feature.description}
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="relative py-20 bg-black/30 backdrop-blur-sm border-t border-gray-800">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
      <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <!-- Left: Steps -->
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 mb-6">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center self-start rounded-full bg-vibe-purple/20 border border-vibe-purple/40 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm text-vibe-purple">
              如何工作
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">
              简单三步，
              <span class="text-vibe-purple">开启音乐情绪之旅</span>
            </h2>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-8">
            {[
              {
                number: '01',
                title: '导入歌单',
                description: '从网易云音乐、QQ音乐或Spotify导入你的歌单，或直接上传本地音乐文件'
              },
              {
                number: '02',
                title: 'AI 情绪分析',
                description: '我们的AI算法会分析每首歌曲的情绪特征，生成详细的情绪报告'
              },
              {
                number: '03',
                title: '探索与享受',
                description: '查看情绪可视化结果，创建基于情绪的播放列表，发现音乐的情感世界'
              }
            ].map((step, index) => (
              <div key={index} class="relative flex gap-6">
                <div class="relative">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-vibe-purple to-vibe-blue flex items-center justify-center text-white font-semibold shrink-0 z-10">
                    {index + 1}
                  </div>
                  {index < 2 && (
                    <div class="absolute top-12 bottom-0 left-1/2 w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-vibe-purple to-transparent transform -translate-x-1/2"></div>
                  )}
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">{step.title}</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">{step.description}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-12 text-6xl font-bold text-vibe-purple/10">
                  {step.number}
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
          <a
            href="/dashboard"
            class="mt-10 self-start inline-flex items-center h-12 px-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-vibe-purple to-vibe-blue hover:from-vibe-blue hover:to-vibe-purple transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg hover:shadow-vibe-purple/30 text-white font-medium"
          >
            立即开始
            <svg class="h-4 w-4 ml-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Platform Support Card -->
        <div>
          <div class="h-full flex flex-col border border-gray-800 bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6">
            <div class="bg-black/60 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center gap-8 h-full">
              <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-vibe-purple/30 to-vibe-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center text-vibe-purple">
                <svg class="h-12 w-12" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19V6l12-3v13M9 19c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zm12-3c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zM9 10l12-3" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">支持的平台</h3>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-8 w-full">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3">
                  <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-red-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-red-400">
                    <svg class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19V6l12-3v13M9 19c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zm12-3c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zM9 10l12-3" />
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">网易云音乐</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3">
                  <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-green-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-green-400">
                    <svg class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19V6l12-3v13M9 19c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zm12-3c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zM9 10l12-3" />
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">QQ音乐</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3">
                  <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400">
                    <svg class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19V6l12-3v13M9 19c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zm12-3c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zM9 10l12-3" />
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Spotify</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Emotion Visualization Preview -->
  <section class="relative py-20 bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-sm border-t border-gray-800">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-8 text-center">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-vibe-purple/20 border border-vibe-purple/40 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm text-vibe-purple">
            情绪可视化
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">
            音乐情绪图谱
          </h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          通过直观的图表，了解音乐的情绪分布，发现歌曲的情感特征
        </p>

        <div class="w-full max-w-3xl">
          <div class="border border-gray-800 bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
            <div class="p-6">
              <div class="aspect-video bg-black/60 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="text-center">
                  <svg class="h-16 w-16 mx-auto text-vibe-purple mb-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
                  </svg>
                  <p class="text-gray-400 mb-2">情绪图谱预览</p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">导入歌单后自动生成</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- Demo emotion bars -->
              <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-6 gap-2">
                {[
                  { label: '快乐', value: 65, color: 'rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.6)' },
                  { label: '悲伤', value: 30, color: 'rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.6)' },
                  { label: '愤怒', value: 15, color: 'rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.6)' },
                  { label: '平静', value: 70, color: 'rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.6)' },
                  { label: '兴奋', value: 60, color: 'rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.6)' },
                  { label: '紧张', value: 25, color: 'rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.6)' }
                ].map((item, index) => (
                  <div key={index} class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
                    <div
                      class="w-full h-2 rounded-full transition-all duration-1000"
                      style={{ backgroundColor: item.color, width: `${item.value}%` }}
                    ></div>
                    <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">{item.label}</span>
                  </div>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <section class="relative py-20 bg-black/30 backdrop-blur-sm border-t border-gray-800">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 flex flex-col gap-12">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-vibe-purple/20 border border-vibe-purple/40 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm text-vibe-purple">
            用户反馈
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">
            用户怎么说
          </h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          来自真实用户的体验分享
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        {[
          {
            name: '李明',
            role: '音乐爱好者',
            quote: 'VibeWeave 让我重新认识了我的音乐库！通过情绪分析，我发现了很多以前忽略的好歌，现在我的播放列表更加符合我的心情了。',
            avatar: 'L'
          },
          {
            name: '张DJ',
            role: '专业DJ',
            quote: '作为一名DJ，VibeWeave 帮助我更好地理解音乐的情绪变化，让我能够创建更加连贯和有情感冲击力的混音。强烈推荐给所有音乐从业者！',
            avatar: 'Z'
          }
        ].map((testimonial, index) => (
          <div
            key={index}
            class="h-full border border-gray-800 bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-vibe-purple/40 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-vibe-purple/5 transition-all duration-300"
          >
            <div class="flex flex-col h-full gap-6">
              <div class="flex gap-1 text-vibe-purple" role="img" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars">
                {[...Array(5)].map((_, i) => (
                  <svg key={i} class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                    <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
                  </svg>
                ))}
              </div>
              <blockquote class="flex-1 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                "{testimonial.quote}"
              </blockquote>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-800">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-vibe-purple to-vibe-blue flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg shrink-0">
                  {testimonial.avatar}
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">{testimonial.name}</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">{testimonial.role}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="relative py-24">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-vibe-purple/20 via-vibe-blue/20 to-vibe-pink/20"></div>
